  <h3 class="anchor-container">
    <a href="#basic-form" class="anchor"><span class="ion-link"></span></a>
    <a name="basic-form" class="anchor-text"></a>
    Basic form
  </h3>

  <hr>

  <div class="sandbox">
    <h5>Edit basic course information</h5>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="control-label">Course title</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Course title" value="An introduction to domain driven development">
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="control-label">Course description</label>
      <p class="help-block">
        To give a good course description with a clear learning objective,
        try to complete the following sentence: "After completing this course,
        learners must be able to...?"
      </p>
      <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Course descripition"></textarea>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% code("html") do %>
  <h5>Edit basic course information</h5>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label class="control-label">Course title</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Course title" value="An introduction to domain driven development">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label class="control-label">Course description</label>
    <p class="help-block">
      To give a good course description with a clear learning objective,
      try to complete the following sentence: "After completing this course,
      learners must be able to...?"
    </p>
    <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Course descripition"></textarea>
  </div>
  <% end %>

  <h3 class="anchor-container">
    <a href="#collapsible-form" class="anchor"><span class="ion-link"></span></a>
    <a name="collapsible-form" class="anchor-text"></a>
    Collapsible form
  </h3>

  <hr>

  <p>
    Try to keep forms as simple as possible. You want the user to fill in everything as
    accurate as possible; so try to reduce the load of work by keeping optional input fields hidden.
  </p>

  <div class="sandbox">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="form-group">
        <div class="col-xs-8">
          <label class="control-label">Paid course</label>
          <p class="help-block no-margin">
            Offer this course for sale.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4">
          <div class="toggle">
            <input class="js-toggle-paid" type="checkbox" data-size="small">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="js-paid-content">
          <div class="col-xs-12">
            <div class="form-collapse">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="control-label">Course price (excl. VAT)</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                  <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0">
                  <span class="input-group-addon is-text">EUR</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group is-last">
                <label class="control-label">Course discount</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                  <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0">
                  <span class="input-group-addon is-text">%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

